title: Softice 4.05 +Patch&Serial
description:
Softice 4.05 W/Patch&Serial, Currently working on my XP Home SP3. It didn't work for me the first time, I pressed Ctrl+D and nothing showed up. You'll have to mess around with the registry keys a bit if this happens. Inside is a registry troubleshooting guide if it gives you this problem too.


After Softice installation follow patch instructions

Patch instructions:
The patch files are the .sys files

Copy the files into this folder:

 C:-WINDOWS-SYSTEM32-DRIVERS 
Overwrite the existing files, restart windows, press Ctrl+D to see if it runs.


Sorry for not including these instructions earlier, my fault.




Please Enjoy.
